	<key>readme</key>
	<string>## Generate Commit Message

Type `commit` followed by a description of your changes. Select a style variant to customize the output.

The generated commit message is copied directly to your clipboard. Press ⌘V to paste it.

### Setup
Enter your OpenAI API key in the workflow configuration.

### Usage
- `commit &lt;description&gt;` — generate a commit message (standard style)
- Select "Generate Commit Message [Conventional]" for Conventional Commits format (feat:, fix:, etc.)
- Select "Generate Commit Message [Detailed]" for a subject + body
- Select "Generate Commit Message [Short]" for an ultra-brief message</string>
